metadata.name: Los Tres Ases
metadata.description:
Taken in Roma Norte, Mexico City on the rooftop of my friend Rodrigo's apartment complex

Rodrigo was showing us (Troy and I) his storage room located on the rooftop that he converted into a tiny studio to play his drums. Right next to this tiny room was this clothesline with three colorful pins that fit the pallet of the beautiful city right behind it

Date: July 31, 2021

Pentax K1000 - Portra 800
